  nodes:
  - question: 'Dhampir: what is this substance...


      you take a closer look
      and i definetly looks out of the ordinary...'
    yesReply: 'you taste the starnge powder on the desk, but it really has no taste.
      but the more you play with it the more you realise it could come from something
      mystical. '
    noReply: 'You bow down to smell it, and as you do a particle of this powder flies
      up into your nose.  you can feel it in your system, and the paranoia raises...
      but nothing more happens. you realise this is probably the work of some creatures
      from your book. '
